com.vmware.vcenter.vm

Class HardwareTypes.Version

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.vapi.bindings.ApiEnumeration<HardwareTypes.Version>
      • com.vmware.vcenter.vm.HardwareTypes.Version
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing interface:
    HardwareTypes

    public static final class HardwareTypes.Version
extends ApiEnumeration<HardwareTypes.Version>
    The Version enumeration class defines the valid virtual hardware versions for a virtual machine. See https://kb.vmware.com/s/article/1003746 (Virtual machine hardware versions (1003746)).

    See enumerated types description.

    See Also:
    Serialized Form
